name: SCARF / HIJAB - Classic
description:
Classic Summer Maxi Scarf
This is one of most beautiful, classy & elegant peaces in my boutique. It is very versatile - erfect for work or even to wear with jeans!

If out of stock - email me & I will reserve one for you!

name: BRACELET - Vintage Berry
description: I absolutely love this one! It looks like a little candy! Gorgeous vintage pink shade beads create lovely look. I have created this gorgeous bracelet to finish any arm candy design that you might have. It is perfect to be worn with a nice watch or on its own.

name: EARRINGS - Elegance
description: This is one of most beautiful peaces I have ever created. very elegant & classy. Glamorous gold colour flower encrusted with swarovski crystals, crowned with brown decorative pearl bead. All sits on the beautiful medium sized artificial pearl. Attached to non allergenic studs.

name: EARRINGS - Nostalgia
description: These earrings were designed by me. This is very elegant yet romantic choice of earrings. This pair was designed from black multi edge beads with medium sized black Swarovski glass bead decorated with Golden colour filigree flower bead cap. Length: 7 cm

name: EARRINGS - Late Summer Dew
description:
These earrings were designed by me. Perfect for romantic evening dinner or whenever you feel in love! 

Gold colour non-allergenic studs, Swarovski pink/purple glass beads, rose patern engraved artificial pears & pink gold colour beads decorated with filigree bead caps. Length: 7cm / 2.6 inch

name: EARRINGS - Wild Child
description:
These earrings were designed by me. Very versatile earrings that could be worn with cowboy jeans & vintage shirt or romantic maxi dress. Perfect for an evening at the cinema or chatty night with your girlfriends!

Made of gold colour leaf charm with beautiful vintage yellow/lime & blue oval shaped beads & berry like turquoise beads hanged on two separate gold colour chains connected to non-allergenic studs. Length: 7 cm

name: EARRINGS - Little Berry
description: These earrings were designed by me. This little pair is made of medium sized golden colour glamorous bead with small Swrovski crystals crown & embroidered with black seed beads filigree bead cap accompanied with small Swarovski black glass bead. Lenght: 2cm/1inch

name: EARRINGS - My Golden Leaf
description:
These earrings were made by me. This wonderful pair is my greatest discovery that gains so many praises. Taking very long to create as each bead has to be selected very carefully to fall into beautiful handmade leaf. Gentle, romantic, classic & outstanding pair that will draw loads of attention & compliments. Beautiful with evening wear. 

This pair was created from many golden colour seed beads & beautified with mate gold colour bead with tiny vintage style bead caps. Attached with non-allergenic hooks. Size & colour of the beads can very upon request to match desired dress! Length: 2.7 cm

name: EARRINGS - Girly Pearly
description:
These earrings were designed by me. Suitable for evening or day wear depends on the way you carry yourself throughout the day!

Its created from medium sized artificial pearl with filigree leaf bead cap embroidered with metallic pink seed beads decorated with see-through pink Swarovski hand painted bead on top. Gold colour hooks are non-allergenic. Custom orders are welcomed. 2.8 cm

name: EARRINGS - Boutique Bow
description:
These earrings were designed by me. Beaded pearl with carefully selected black & golden seed beads decorated with tiny black lace creates playful yet elegant look.

Made of small black & golden beads, antique style bead caps & black lace attached to non-allergenic hooks. Available in wide range of seed beads & laces upon request. Length: 2.5cm/1.1 inch

name: NECKLACE - My Dream Come True
description:
This is one of its kind necklaces. I made only one of these. It is long enough to be seen while you wearing a hijab. Carefully selected & beaded ribbons together with the golden colour filigrie heart pendant  creates romantic & very chic look. 

Lenght of a necklace hanging is 50cm (or 95cm around the neck).

name: HEADBAND - Hot Pink
description:
This headband was handmade by me with loads of love to our little princesses! Measuring 15,5" or 39 cm it suits new born and comfortably stretches to adult size without giving headaches & feels light as you wear it.

If out of stock - please email me & I will make one for you!

If you have a dress & want custom headband to match it - please message me :)
